<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">To be fair, sometimes private-market valuation=
s do go down. For instance a lot of big=C2=A0private companies have public =
mutual funds as investors, and those funds periodically report the carrying=
 value of their private stakes, and they are a bit more aggressive about ma=
rking them down.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-6" style=3D"c=
olor: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; =
border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; backgro=
und-color: transparent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[6]</span>
</a> Here is a fun little <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/30154092.261520/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYXhpb3MuY29tLzIwMjIvMTIvMzAvdHdpdHR=
lci1maWRlbGl0eS12YWx1YXRpb24/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB336ab8af" itemprop=3D=
"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0000=
00; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bott=
om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> va=
luation puzzle</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fidelity slashed its carrying value of Twitter=
 by 56% during the first month of Elon Musk's ownership, according to a new=
 disclosure.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Driving the news: Fidelity was among the group=
 of outside investors that helped Musk finance his $44 billion takeover of =
the social media site, by purchasing equity. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fidelity's Contrafund valued its Twitter share=
s at $53.47 million on Oct. 31, which was just days after Musk's deal close=
d. It then revalued the shares at around $23.46 million as of Nov. 30, repr=
esenting a 56% decline.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Let=E2=80=99s say you are in charge of marking=
 Fidelity=E2=80=99s illiquid private investments to market. What do you kno=
w about the value of your Twitter stake?</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You know that Musk paid about $44 bil=
lion for Twitter in October, and some of your funds went in on the deal wit=
h him.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You know that, at the time,=
 Musk said he was =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/30154092.261520/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbG=
VzLzIwMjItMTAtMTkvZWxvbi1tdXNrLXNheXMtaGUtcy1vYnZpb3VzbHktb3ZlcnBheWluZy1mb=
3ItdHdpdHRlcj9jbXBpZD1CQkQwMTA0MjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0=
bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzAxMDQmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R=
1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBa6cd6689" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D=
"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: non=
e !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; borde=
r-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">obviously overpaying</a>=E2=
=80=9D for Twitter.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">You know that,=
 since Musk agreed to pay $44 billion for Twitter, tech stocks have broadly=
